            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1586950301049-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse your <strong>blanched edamame beans</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>edamame beans</strong> to a bowl and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1 min, or until hot and cooked with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>edamame beans </strong>and add them to a bowl with your<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>– these are your<strong> sesame edamame beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1586950310404-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
