            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1586950340954-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into the pot and cook for 1-2 min, mixing vigorously, until firm and scrambled</p><p>Tip: Try scrambling the egg with chopsticks if you have some!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
