            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Arrange the <strong>sushi rice</strong>, <strong>fragrant Japanese-style pork</strong>, <strong>sesame edamame beans</strong> and <strong>scrambled egg </strong>in bowls</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>shichimi togarashi </strong>all over (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
